{"id":"3360751622","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/3360751622","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMzM2MDc1MTYyMg==","status":"current","title":"Proceso de Carga de PTOs","version":{"by":{"type":"known","accountId":"712020:739e890c-1511-42c4-897d-b8d9d11ae918","accountType":"atlassian","email":"","publicName":"Agustin Llado","profilePicture":{"path":"/wiki/aa-avatar/712020:739e890c-1511-42c4-897d-b8d9d11ae918","width":48,"height":48,"isDefault":false},"displayName":"Agustin Llado","isExternalCollaborator":false,"isGuest":false,"locale":"en_GB","accountStatus":"active","_expandable":{"operations":"","personalSpace":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/user?accountId=712020:739e890c-1511-42c4-897d-b8d9d11ae918"}},"when":"2024-09-18T14:15:36.911Z","friendlyWhen":"Sep 18, 2024","message":"","number":2,"minorEdit":false,"ncsStepVersion":"2704","ncsStepVersionSource":"ncs-ack","confRev":"confluence$content$3360751622.29","contentTypeModified":false,"_expandable":{"collaborators":"","content":"/rest/api/content/3360751622"},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3360751622/version/2"}},"ancestors":[{"id":"2178416778","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2178416778","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjE3ODQxNjc3OA==","status":"current","title":"Bancard","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":878},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}},{"id":"2260140085","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2260140085","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjI2MDE0MDA4NQ==","status":"current","title":"Management","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":504478064},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2260140085/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2260140085/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2260140085/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2260140085/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2260140085","tinyui":"/x/NQC3hg","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2260140085","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2260140085/Management","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2260140085"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"452435aa-d823-4826-9f7a-6a90a746ec6f\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Este documento detalla los pasos a seguir al momento de cargar un PTO (vacaciones, estudio, enfermedad, etc..), as&iacute; mejoramos la planificaci&oacute;n desde nuestro lado, y le damos visibilidad a Bancard de los d&iacute;as en los que no vamos a estar disponibles.</p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Notificar a <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"5ad8f697d8b95a2b34f27719\" ri:local-id=\"8c137fdb-faae-4da2-bc2c-dd15e00f083d\" /></ac:link> / <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"712020:739e890c-1511-42c4-897d-b8d9d11ae918\" ri:local-id=\"f893cac2-17f4-4e5f-9bea-9d02c1218b20\" /></ac:link> sobre las fechas que se solicitan, en lo posible con un tiempo moderado de aviso previo de 2 semanas para licencias cortas, y 1 / 2 meses para licencias largas. Esto no es obligatorio, pero si nos permite acomodar el equipo y las iniciativas, y tambi&eacute;n evaluar el tema de budget con el equipo de Allocations / Operaciones por si hay que conseguir un suplente para esas fechas. </p></li><li><p>Cargar las fechas en HiBob</p><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Desde la Home de <a href=\"https://app.hibob.com/\">HiBob</a> vamos a seleccionar la opci&oacute;n <em>Request Time Off </em></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"156\" ac:original-width=\"395\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:width=\"395\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"Screenshot 2024-09-17 at 2.33.55 PM.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p /></li><li><p>Seleccionamos tipo de PTO que vamos a solicitar </p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"543\" ac:original-width=\"488\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:width=\"292\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"Screenshot 2024-09-17 at 2.34.30 PM.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p /></li><li><p>Seleccionamos la fecha deseada </p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"427\" ac:original-width=\"446\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:width=\"446\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"Screenshot 2024-09-17 at 2.35.29 PM.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p /></li><li><p>Le damos <em>Submit</em>, y queda cargada la solicitud de PTO</p><p /></li></ol></li><li><p>Por &uacute;ltimo, antes de irnos, vamos a cargar en <em>Teams</em> nuestro estado de PTO, para darle visibilidad al equipo, para que tengan en cuenta que no estamos conectados, ya que ellos no tienen acceso a nuestro HiBob ni nuestros calendarios. </p><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>En la ventana de Teams, hacemos click al &iacute;cono de nuestro perfil en el lado superior izquierdo y seleccionamos <em>Set Status Message </em></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"343\" ac:original-width=\"319\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:width=\"319\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"Screenshot 2024-09-18 at 11.08.54 AM.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p /></li><li><p>Escribimos un mensaje que queremos que se muestre mientras estamos de PTO. <strong>Importante en el mensaje incluir la fecha de regreso. </strong><br /><em>PTO por estudio / enfermedad / vacaciones hasta XX/XX/XXXX</em><br />Seleccionamos tambi&eacute;n la opci&oacute;n <em>Show when people message me</em>, y <em>Clear status message after &lt;Custom&gt;, con la fecha de regreso.</em></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"572\" ac:original-width=\"324\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:width=\"324\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"Screenshot 2024-09-18 at 11.07.58 AM.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p>  </p></li><li><p>Seleccionamos <em>Done </em>y queda prontooo, a disfrutar las vacaciones \uD83D\uDE0E</p><p> </p><p> </p></li></ol></li></ol>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3360751622"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":370},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3360751622/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3360751622/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3360751622/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3360751622/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3360751622","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3360751622/Proceso+de+Carga+de+PTOs","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3360751622","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3360751622","tinyui":"/x/BgBRy","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}